 ğŸ”¥ Final One-Liner (Interview Ready)

> AWS VPC architecture isolates network using public & private subnets, controls traffic via route tables, secures access using security groups, 
and provides internet connectivity through IGW and NAT while ensuring high availability using multiple AZs.

